Cache Invalidation Strategy. Triggers: 1) Prompt Change -> Invalidate All Caches (Version in Cache Key). 2) Model Update -> Invalidate Semantic + Response Cache. 3) TTL Expiry -> Auto-evict (FAQ: 24h, Status: 5min). 4) Data Update (RAG) -> Invalidate Related Semantic Entries. 5) Manual Purge Button for Emergencies. Visual: Cache layers with invalidation arrows, version numbers on keys. German labels.